OL,3,CWoman found drowned named by police
OL,5,FA woman who was found drowned in
OL,6,FHenley-on-Thames has been named by
OL,7,Fpolice as 44-year-old Jennifer Symonds.
OL,9,FMs Symonds' body was found by officers
OL,10,Fin Phyllis Court Drive, in the town,
OL,11,Fon Friday (6 March).
OL,13,FA formal identification will take
OL,14,Fplace at a later date and police say
OL,15,FMs Symonds' next of kin are being
OL,16,Fsupported by specially trained family
OL,17,Fliaison officers.
